rows.label: qst000101_msg001
rows.name: Bother, bother...

rows.label: qst000101_msg002
rows.name: Can't use Nopon as muscle...

rows.label: qst000101_msg003
rows.name: And I can't just ask the Superbians...

rows.label: qst000101_msg004
rows.name: Mm? Oh, hi. Well, actually...

rows.label: qst000101_msg005
rows.name:
I've got some cargo in the harbor that
I brought from Invidia to trade, but...

rows.label: qst000101_msg006
rows.name: It's an ever-so-slight nuisance...

rows.label: qst000101_msg007
rows.name: What shall we ask?

rows.label: qst000101_msg008
rows.name: Ask if someone's causing trouble

rows.label: qst000101_msg009
rows.name: Ask if the cargo is illegal

rows.label: qst000101_msg010
rows.name: That's a good guess!

rows.label: qst000101_msg011
rows.name: Except it's not exactly a person...

rows.label: qst000101_msg012
rows.name: Ah, no, nothing like that!

rows.label: qst000101_msg013
rows.name: I don't have the stomach for crime.

rows.label: qst000101_msg014
rows.name:
It seems that Trent Krabbles
love the stuff I'm transporting.

rows.label: qst000101_msg015
rows.name:
To get to it, they clamber on deck and
try to steal the cargo...

rows.label: qst000101_msg016
rows.name:
I hired some goons to stand guard,
but they all got done in.

rows.label: qst000101_msg017
rows.name:
So I'm out here now, looking for
someone to replace 'em with...

rows.label: qst000101_msg018
rows.name:
But I'm having no luck so far,
so it's starting to feel a bit dire...

rows.label: qst000101_msg019
rows.name: You're saying you'll take the job?

rows.label: qst000101_msg020
rows.name:
Thanks a bunch, pal!
You're one in a million!

rows.label: qst000101_msg021
rows.name:
The cargo's in Goldmund Return Port.
It's pretty large, you can't miss it.

rows.label: qst000101_msg022
rows.name:
It'd be great if you could chase off the
thieving Trent Krabbles!

rows.label: qst000101_msg023
rows.name: Thanks in advance!
